FAQ_SUBTITLE_PLACEHOLDER_TEXT: Everything you need to know about our rubber duck emporium
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_1: What types of rubber ducks do you offer?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_1: We offer a wide variety of rubber ducks, including classic yellow ducks, themed ducks (like superhero or holiday designs), and custom-made ducks tailored to your specifications.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_2: Are your rubber ducks safe for children?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_2: Absolutely! All our rubber ducks are made from non-toxic materials and undergo rigorous safety testing to ensure they're suitable for all ages, including infants and young children.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_3: Yes, we ship our rubber ducks worldwide! Shipping costs and delivery times vary depending on your location. You can get a quote during the checkout process.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_4: Can I create a custom rubber duck design?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_4: Certainly! We offer a custom duck design service where you can choose colors, add accessories, and even create ducks with your company logo. Contact our support team for more details.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_5: We offer a 30-day return policy for unused, undamaged ducks in their original packaging. Custom-designed ducks are non-refundable unless there's a manufacturing defect.
PLACEHOLDER_FAQ_TITLE: Quack Your Questions: Rubber Duck FAQs
ACCORDION_QUESTION_1: What types of rubber ducks do you offer?
ACCORDION_ANSWER_1: We offer a wide variety of rubber ducks, including classic yellow ducks, themed ducks (such as professions or characters), and limited edition collectibles. Our selection caters to both casual enthusiasts and serious collectors.
ACCORDION_QUESTION_2: Are your rubber ducks safe for children?
ACCORDION_ANSWER_2: Yes, all our rubber ducks are made from non-toxic materials and comply with international safety standards. However, we recommend adult supervision for children under 3 years old.
ACCORDION_ANSWER_3: Absolutely! We ship our quacky friends worldwide. Shipping costs and delivery times vary depending on your location. You can calculate shipping fees at checkout.
ACCORDION_ANSWER_4: We offer a 30-day return policy for unused, undamaged items in their original packaging. If you're not 100% satisfied with your rubber duck, simply contact our customer service team to initiate a return or exchange.
